item.title: A quick question!
item.dc:creator: @X_Entinity_X X Entinity X
item.description:
@X_Entinity_X wrote:

Are you useing Delta? if so go to gui.java and search whatever the ip is now, probaly 127.0.0.1 <-- change that to what the ip you want, then compile and run.

If Project Insanity, go into client.java and search server = then change: server = “127.0.0.1”, the 127.0.0.1 to whatever you want, compile and run.

Need any other information, private message me.
